{"tid":484102,"cid":31,"subCid":0,"title":"【年尾啦又要出Board Game】今次有請 Edward Snowden（斯諾登）","createTime":"2017-11-29T19:02:24.000Z","updateTime":"2017-12-16T17:42:27.000Z","uid":46784,"like":18,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":15,"replies":[{"pid":"83fb417eb58cc96e2c5c8848cb89d4039b3ad903","tid":484102,"uid":46784,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-29T19:02:24.000Z","msg":"是咁的，大約三個月前我地開始整緊隻Board game<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ，搵過畫師，大改左不下十次<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 。依家上黎獻下醜，大家見笑鳥<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 。 <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/11/30/012846_94e6d906664d5dbf3392ee87fd23e3ee.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F11%2F30%2F012846_94e6d906664d5dbf3392ee87fd23e3ee.jpg&h=ad838ea9&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n咁隻GAME叫「Snowden（斯諾登）」，每人扮演一個角色，以不擇手段但求達到目的，包括政苦、記者、偵探，當然最後唔少得主角斯諾登，<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 。 <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/11/30/014559_d004eef369f69ad5550dd5ef2971f0ff.jpeg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F11%2F30%2F014559_d004eef369f69ad5550dd5ef2971f0ff.jpeg&h=a513ce86&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/11/30/025654_c26e92bad77e4ceea95cfc4be09b7b79.jpeg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F11%2F30%2F025654_c26e92bad77e4ceea95cfc4be09b7b79.jpeg&h=b12153a4&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n（少少背景：史諾登，前美國中央情報局職員，美國國家安全局外包技術員。因於2013年6月在香港將美國國家安全局稜鏡計劃的秘密文件披露給了《衛報》和《華盛頓郵報》，遭到通緝。2013年6月23日，史諾登離開香港前往莫斯科，俄羅斯給予他一年臨時難民身分。）<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/11/30/014133_246776640861847edc83d228c7e9320e.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F11%2F30%2F014133_246776640861847edc83d228c7e9320e.jpg&h=d421cde3&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n斯諾登<br />\n主要目標是避開政府的捉拿，並在地圖上留下要公開的信息給記者，在解密時把自己在地圖上放置分置信息的位置轉為密碼給記者。<br />\n<br />\n政苦<br />\n目標是在地圖上盡快捉拿斯諾登，在解密上盡量堵截位置資訊。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/11/30/025410_736a1c2221199a858017f34030b165cc.jpeg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F11%2F30%2F025410_736a1c2221199a858017f34030b165cc.jpeg&h=61c402b2&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n記者<br />\n主要目標是要在地圖上獲得資料，並把它公開，在地圖上也要幫助告密者避開政府，在解密環節要去獲得斯諾登正確的資料擺放位置。<br />\n<br />\n偵探<br />\n目標和記者目標相同, 在地圖上獲得正確的資料，並把它公開，但她是為政府工作的,所以公開後不會導致斯諾登勝利<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/11/30/014648_a317250582c91b4c871e184007519b3d.jpeg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F11%2F30%2F014648_a317250582c91b4c871e184007519b3d.jpeg&h=2e4815b1&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n想大家比下意見，想個Game再包含咩？（玩法、配件、精品 etc.）<br />\n<br />\n上Facebook留個名：<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/csTheWorldCouncil/ \" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2FcsTheWorldCouncil%2F%20&d=iVdJo81XXU2rHDVppMyVTEbWhtBCnEJYRTWbVbFBOac%3D&h=7dc69840\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/csTheWorldCouncil/ </a>"},{"pid":"aef45a32d5987a2869a7a91d76f9ea4de79cdb06","tid":484102,"uid":21310,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-30T00:39:13.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"ceadd6a740a833405c1c636257fcd04b3bde2a39","tid":484102,"uid":38899,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-30T00:44:32.000Z","msg":"我地有無得試玩先"},{"pid":"ae87af10f83c5448aa2bffc62326383045d734d0","tid":484102,"uid":145817,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-30T01:20:17.000Z","msg":"又有game要衝出香港了<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6f465825b4de3097868d1b2876b2c3d407b22fbf","tid":484102,"uid":25385,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-30T01:26:40.000Z","msg":"world council仲會唔會整<br />\ncold war個擴充包又點？ <br />\n係你地專頁問野又十問九唔應"},{"pid":"3f533ceab14cca7241be88c5ef052026d75b60e9","tid":484102,"uid":46784,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-30T09:49:42.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>world council仲會唔會整<br />\ncold war個擴充包又點？ <br />\n係你地專頁問野又十問九唔應</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n因為訂太細d廠唔嗲唔吊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n但係我地又唔夠錢做大張單<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cfed1370458adec694ab453cc42cfbbb959f9242","tid":484102,"uid":46784,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-30T09:50:31.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>我地有無得試玩先</blockquote><br />\n有啊 好快公佈時間<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4764fc4c6f792869be4c6ca3b260ca733d9ed4ef","tid":484102,"uid":1714,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-30T12:27:21.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a53676cce5461151ab71ac67b2070f13734a5e9b","tid":484102,"uid":46784,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-30T16:30:07.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"4a4d37b7b376297f78549c45a3518215388978f6","tid":484102,"uid":46784,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-30T18:23:57.000Z","msg":"想大家比下意見，想個Game再包含咩？（玩法、配件、精品 etc.）<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/photo.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7c7e9c30410d9bd18ed951b29686daff07a291b8","tid":484102,"uid":46784,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-30T18:25:29.000Z","msg":"有無人睇過 第四公民 Citizenfour 條紀錄片？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b9e1888839d51291db95024e423340aaa4d86887","tid":484102,"uid":53922,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-30T18:27:56.000Z","msg":"有無打算放上kickstarter? 迴響應該大好多"},{"pid":"a5a752ec377ce28ee81be670ff4f5703971c4b43","tid":484102,"uid":46784,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-30T18:30:55.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>有無打算放上kickstarter? 迴響應該大好多</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n舊登時代我地放過一隻上kickstarter，都多得巴絲打支持先出到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a182cc80f6826ce931bf0dd1720452954e1d13a1","tid":484102,"uid":50144,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-30T18:50:23.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>有無人睇過 第四公民 Citizenfour 條紀錄片？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n有冇睇埋John Oliver同佢做嗰個訪問？"},{"pid":"42bc765fed81a911310705eea3197fe64b32b99c","tid":484102,"uid":46784,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-30T18:54:22.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>有無人睇過 第四公民 Citizenfour 條紀錄片？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n有冇睇埋John Oliver同佢做嗰個訪問？</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=XEVlyP4_11M\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DXEVlyP4_11M&d=iVdJo81XXU2rHDVppMyVTEbWhtBCnEJYRTWbVbFBOac%3D&h=0a97d23c\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=XEVlyP4_11M</a><br />\n<br />\n呢條？好似好耐之後先出<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n仲有參考電影<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"786c56d4576737c9c828772f127106e4db218ff3","tid":484102,"uid":46784,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-30T18:56:54.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>有無人睇過 第四公民 Citizenfour 條紀錄片？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n有冇睇埋John Oliver同佢做嗰個訪問？</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=XEVlyP4_11M\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DXEVlyP4_11M&d=iVdJo81XXU2rHDVppMyVTEbWhtBCnEJYRTWbVbFBOac%3D&h=0a97d23c\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=XEVlyP4_11M</a><br />\n<br />\n呢條？好似好耐之後先出<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n仲有參考電影<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n&quot;The only time you can be completely free from risk is when you're in prison.&quot;<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f1240b108140d5f46407e048236f05d3ef3ffd31","tid":484102,"uid":50144,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-30T19:10:13.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>有無人睇過 第四公民 Citizenfour 條紀錄片？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n有冇睇埋John Oliver同佢做嗰個訪問？</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=XEVlyP4_11M\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DXEVlyP4_11M&d=iVdJo81XXU2rHDVppMyVTEbWhtBCnEJYRTWbVbFBOac%3D&h=0a97d23c\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=XEVlyP4_11M</a><br />\n<br />\n呢條？好似好耐之後先出<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n仲有參考電影<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n&quot;The only time you can be completely free from risk is when you're in prison.&quot;<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n係，喺佢去到俄羅斯之後一段時間先做嘅。<br />\n呢段好睇在換個例子之後，啲人對件事嘅反應有幾唔同。"},{"pid":"403b5d7270f3388e53cffd2871c259cbd3c624ae","tid":484102,"uid":46784,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-01T15:23:07.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"efc79816dc6f6158df1bad8f0472964436d8f520","tid":484102,"uid":46784,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-01T15:28:16.000Z","msg":"史諾登表示之所以來到香港泄密和接受採訪是<strong>因為香港有保護言論自由和異議分子人權的承諾</strong>，是地球上為數不多的可以抵抗美國政府勢力的地方，而且自己「有從擁有共同價值觀的國家尋求庇護的傾向」。<br />\n<br />\n<strong>由於香港酒店昂貴</strong>，「他的信用卡很快就會超出使用限額」。史諾登居住的美麗華酒店宣布史諾登在當日已經退房。同日早上，何謝韋律師事務所的文浩正律師接到一個電話，讓史諾登藏身在位於荔枝角斯里蘭卡難民家中，一星期後轉移到深水埗及位於堅尼地城的<strong>劏房</strong>，<strong>因香港社會不重視該群體，較為安全</strong>。<br />\n<br />\n更多背景<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2b621b8a70ced6f1756def2ea3b44edab746bdf0","tid":484102,"uid":46784,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-02T10:24:13.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"f94610f2b29809335b8f13aa2467855275187343","tid":484102,"uid":46784,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-02T10:28:23.000Z","msg":"仲有無人知/記得斯諾登，其實到過香港？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2c277dd0fcb8324490c813c061b3fd3e3473a768","tid":484102,"uid":144854,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-02T16:01:13.000Z","msg":"記得呀 佢黎過香港一排又再走呀嘛"},{"pid":"b0ac21912ffbf6aabb91103b66041071b038b13e","tid":484102,"uid":132289,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-02T16:14:36.000Z","msg":"lm"},{"pid":"56c43282689ddabc2add0c63df45c4e36c086ba3","tid":484102,"uid":46784,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-03T03:32:39.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>記得呀 佢黎過香港一排又再走呀嘛</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n所有野都係香港爆<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ab285949fc0ab5a1c58b6fe5c810317c5bd0f4f2","tid":484102,"uid":46784,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-03T03:38:18.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/12/03/113751_610ccda130b32de3a9039869273c6762.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F12%2F03%2F113751_610ccda130b32de3a9039869273c6762.jpg&h=05e99a6e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n諗住做封面<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}